{"tid":2123021,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【分手邊緣】啲人玩少一陣狼人殺係咪會死？","createTime":"2020-07-24T10:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T05:46:07.000Z","uid":363834,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8669272cb8d6ff0a8aee97cdee5f51780a1adcaa","tid":2123021,"uid":363834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"男朋友同我都好鍾意玩狼...<br />\n以前睇開娛百覺得好得意...<br />\n慢慢佢帶我去唔同boardgame店到玩...<br />\n本來都冇咩嘢...<br />\n<br />\n近排爆第三波我唔夠膽出街...<br />\n心裡面都唔想佢出咁多街...<br />\n但係又唔想好似我某d姐妹咁落禁足令畀男朋友...<br />\n平時我哋去開嗰間都因為有事停咗營業...<br />\n點知佢仲要去其他地方玩...<br />\n一來擔心疫情會惹到佢...(因為d人玩時會太激動會唔戴口罩)<br />\n二來又擔心佢會惹到d狂風浪蝶...(佢靚仔我平凡)<br />\n同佢講過好多次都唔聽...又話冇咁易中招...<br />\n我唔去佢自己去咁...<br />\n我唔想變做狼人殺群組啊...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yiffjbn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiffjbn.jpg&h=5bba4a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHtkvh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHtkvh2.jpg&h=9d5aecd6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢間嘢咁唔負責任...有咩方法可以處理?"},{"pid":"98084e083e626a16dbc248fa24ed9ab1e83435f8","tid":2123021,"uid":201414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"一齊上去除罩咳 輕鬆攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113462410e754a43cea761cb71ceb2fcd4d51bb","tid":2123021,"uid":165482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"829f893eef51c231039b8687f8ece2ed7000dc4f","tid":2123021,"uid":363834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1113462410e754a43cea761cb71ceb2fcd4d51bb","tid":2123021,"uid":165482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d949408ec6979bb1ff8bc5521ea87e0bcadfe","tid":2123021